<section id="content">

<h1>Michael Hedges</h1>
<ul>

	<li><blockquote cite="/t/2713">
	<q>I’m not trying to play the guitar. I’m trying to play music.</q>
	<cite><a href="/t/2713">Michael Hedges</a></cite>
</blockquote>

</li>

	<li><blockquote cite="/t/2016">
	<q>I play guitar because it lets me dream out loud.</q>
	<cite><a href="/t/2016">Michael Hedges</a></cite>
</blockquote>

</li>

	<li><blockquote cite="/t/432">
	<q>The mind must be trained to follow the flow of the heart&#39;s river.</q>
	<cite><a href="/t/432">Michael Hedges</a></cite>
</blockquote>

</li>

	<li><blockquote cite="/t/320">
	<q>Being sure of yourself is the best advice I can think of.  Having fun and not going too fast are important, but being self-assured will keep you composing for the longest period of time. <br> <br>The minute I lose my sense of self-worth is the same minute I turn on a  movie, take a break, eat, etc.</q>
	<cite><a href="/t/320">Michael Hedges</a></cite>
</blockquote>

</li>

</ul>
